From: Yuki Sireneva <yuki.utk8g@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 3 Apr 2026 03:10:55 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Control calls with MPRIS

- play, pause, play-pause -> accept
- next, prev, stop, quit -> hangup

Report call state as playback state in MPRIS
State mapping:
* WaitingUserConfirmation, Busy -> Stopped
* ExchangingKeys, Established -> Playing
* everything else -> Paused

Co-Authored-By: Sonya Sireneva <sleirsgoevy@gmail.com>
---
 Telegram/SourceFiles/calls/calls_instance.cpp | 100 +++++++++++++++++-
 Telegram/SourceFiles/calls/calls_instance.h   |   9 ++
 .../settings/settings_experimental.cpp        |   2 +
 3 files changed, 110 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/Telegram/SourceFiles/calls/calls_instance.cpp b/Telegram/SourceFiles/calls/calls_instance.cpp
index 42c7806086..2b66813668 100644
--- a/Telegram/SourceFiles/calls/calls_instance.cpp
